    "tip_3_title": "Don't over-thin",
    "tip_3_text": "Respect the natural thickness of your brow; over-plucking takes months to recover.",
    "tip_4_title": "The pencil trick",
    "tip_4_text": "Measure the start from your nostril, the arch passing the pupil, and the end at the corner of the eye.",
    "tip_5_title": "Set with clear gel",
    "tip_5_text": "Even if you don't use color, a gel keeps hairs in place all day.",
    "tip_6_title": "Beware of darkness",
