    "tip_7_title": "Short strokes",
    "tip_7_text": "When using pencil or pomade, make fine strokes emulating hairs in the direction of growth.",
    "tip_8_title": "Better to highlight by day",
    "tip_8_text": "For daily makeup, avoid concealer that's too white under the brow.",
    "tip_9_title": "Avoid dyeing without experience",
    "tip_9_text": "Tint or henna lasts weeks; if it's your first time, go to a professional.",
    "tip_10_title": "Exfoliate the skin",
