    "tip_11_title": "Monthly maintenance",
    "tip_11_text": "Plucking only what's necessary every 3-4 weeks prevents losing or damaging the main shape.",
    "tip_12_title": "Sleep on your back",
    "tip_12_text": "Avoid friction with the pillow; it can cause hair loss on the brow tails.",
